xonsh (0.6.3+dfsg-1) unstable; urgency=medium

    As of version 0.6.2, static configuration files
    (XDG_CONFIG_HOME/xonsh/config.json) have been deprecated, and executable
    xonshrc files are now the only supported config mechanism.

    The default search path for xonshrc files is /etc/xonshrc,
    XDG_CONFIG_HOME/xonsh/rc.xsh, ~/.xonshrc

 -- Gordon Ball <gordon@chronitis.net>  Wed, 02 May 2018 07:55:33 +0000
